9. Creating Fact Table and Populating data

Facts: Marketing Conversions

T-SQL Script step by step to create Fact tables then populate them with appropriate test values.

Creating Fact table to hold all the tracking entries of previous marketing conversions with appropriate foreign key columns which refer to primary key column of the dimensions. Then, it needs to be taking care of while populating the fact table to refer to primary key values of appropriate dimensions.
